<item>
            <title>[LU-3257] IO framework and Readonly replication file</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3257</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Revise CLIO to support read only replication file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following features will be implemented in this task:&lt;br/&gt;
1. timeout IO RPC support&lt;br/&gt;
2. IO framework to try next replica to fetch data&lt;br/&gt;
3. policy to choose replica to serve read&lt;br/&gt;
4. dynamic cl_page. Fanout page won&apos;t be implemented in this phase, but dynamic cl_page, which can link a top page to different sub page by replica selection has to be worked out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
